      "message": "[info] Line 180: Performance suggestion: reserve result capacity before appending and avoid repeated ConfigurationManager lookups when possible. Rationale: convertVecMap/docs.size() is known and reserving avoids reallocations; calling collaborativeDocumentName() for every document may be an IPC/query — consider using commit-provided displayName as primary or batching name lookups. Suggested change:\n```suggestion\nresult.reserve(static_cast\u003cint\u003e(docs.size()));\n// prefer commit displayName when possible and only query collaborativeDocumentName() if necessary\n```",
