      "message": "[warning] Line 64: Behavioral concern: the optimization prevents rescanning for editable documents while hasEditableDocuments is true. This reduces repeated scans but may cause the UI to miss updates if documents are deleted/renamed elsewhere (daemon-side) and the flag isn\u0027t cleared. Rationale: external changes to conversation documents may require re-evaluation. Suggested improvements: add explicit hooks to clear hasEditableDocuments on conversation switch, on focus, or add a periodic light refresh. Example suggestion:\n```suggestion\n// Consider calling updateHasEditableDocuments() also on conversation change or window focus\nConnections { target: ConversationsModel; function onCurrentChanged() { messageBarRowLayout.hasEditableDocuments \u003d false; messageBarRowLayout.updateHasEditableDocuments(); } }\n```",
